rows.label: tlk43310148_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Queen Lagert's kinda mellowed
out a bit. Not sure if I like it.

rows.label: tlk43310148_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I was pretty shocked that she accepted
that ceasefire from the Superbians.

rows.label: tlk43310148_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Iira may have been up to no good,
but it was still the Superbians who dug
up that Judician Divine Beast weapon.

rows.label: tlk43310148_04_msg0004
rows.name:
It was their fault. I dunno how we can
just let them off the hook like that?

rows.label: tlk43310148_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Maybe it's 'cos that Superbian Blade
saved the Queen.

rows.label: tlk43310148_04_msg0006
rows.name:
But I can't help wondering if the
Superbians didn't cook up that
little drama themselves...
